6:
Today's concert is going to be so
much fun, Tae-chan!
20:
Well... Everything turned out okay so
far, right?
26:
That's right. Tae-chan's really up to
the challenge.
41:
Then again, I suppose we only need
to provide support.
50:
*sigh* How I've grown accustomed
to this...
57:
Thank you so much for showing up
today, everyone!
66:
We're going to party it up as
Number 0 and Number 1! Here's
hoping you'll follow along!
74:
Their movements could not be more
out of sync... And those sluggish
movements are the epitome of
zombiehood!
76:
I grow extremely wary! Our support
does not extend to their onstage
performance!
80:
By this point, the townspeople are
probably used to their quirks.
87:
I mean, even you find Franchouchou
to be an entertaining group, don't
you?
90:
Indeed... I do consider myself their
ally after all.
92:
Then surely it's only natural for the
audience to feel the same way.
96:
I've been doing plenty of jobs with
Number 0 lately.
98:
Anyone happen to come by our
sales event the other day?
103:
Thank you so much! Aren't we such
a lucky pair, Number 0?!
109: I went to the photo op!
113: Really?! You fans are the best!
116:
And the best fans deserve the best
possible show we can put on! Let's
gooo!
122:
Louder now, come on! Say it like you
mean it!
135:
My goodness! What was that
sudden scream about?
149: C'mon, Light. You give it a try too.
169:
What have I just witnessed... More
importantly, I'm bushed from all that
screaming.
172:
Same. My throat's all dry from that
death metal screaming session in
the second half.
178:
Great work, you two! Thanks for
pitching in back there!
182:
Ahaha... Glad we were able to fake it
well enough.
193:
Was that a "thank you"? Well, you're
welcome.
197:
I still don't understand you well, but
it's become clear to me that you
care for your friends.
199:
Keep up the good work. For I will be
cheering you on.
213:
Ahaha, Tae-chan! Biting's not
always the best way to express your
joy, okay?
